  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "After Typhos Prime, Lieutenant Kage is rotting in Imperial detention when Colonel Schaeffer offers him the Last Chancers' usual bargain: useful death instead of useless death. This time the target is a Tau Empire commander, and the cover is an Imperial diplomatic delegation received as honored guests on a Tau world. Kage and a small condemned team must play at civility long enough to position the kill, while Schaeffer keeps the true shape of the mission hidden until retreat is almost fantasy. A lean heist-procedural with satirical diplomatic teeth.",
